  "common": {
    "name": {
      "zh": "7.62x51毫米 BPZ FMJ",
      "en": "7.62x51mm BCP FMJ"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "BPZ FMJ",
      "en": "BCP FMJ"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "跳蚤市场: 426₽ | 物品价值: 240 | Mechanic报价: 134₽购买渠道 @ Jaeger 等级3 < 252₽\n购买渠道 @ 莲花 等级2 < 2$ ≈ 270₽\n\n制作要求 x120 @ 工作台 等级2 < 火药 x2 | Σ 每个物品 ≈ 278₽\n\n7.62x51 毫米 BPZ FMJ 弹药，配有重 10.9 克的铅芯弹头，外覆双金属被甲，采用钢质弹壳。该款弹药由俄罗斯巴尔瑙尔弹药制造厂 (BCP) 生产，主要用于狩猎、自卫以及打靶用途。尽管这是一款民用弹药，BPZ FMJ 的停止作用与穿甲能力都相当突出，能够轻松穿透中低等级的护甲。",
      "en": "跳蚤市场: 426₽ | 物品价值: 240 | Mechanic报价: 134₽购买渠道 @ Jaeger 等级3 < 252₽\n购买渠道 @ 莲花 等级2 < 2$ ≈ 270₽\n\n制作要求 x120 @ 工作台 等级2 < 火药 x2 | Σ 每个物品 ≈ 278₽\n\nA 7.62x51mm BCP FMJ cartridge with a 10.9 gram lead core bullet with a bimetallic jacket in a steel case; intended for hunting, home defense, and target practice, produced by Barnaul Cartridge Plant. Despite its rudimentary design, this cartridge is capable of providing an outstanding stopping power effect, as well as being able to pierce through basic ballistic body protections as well as some intermediate models."
    },
